    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      563.99,
      534.05,
      608.45
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central, Sabaragamuwa, Uva and North-central provinces and in Kurunegala and Vavuniya districts during the early hours of the morning.",
